---
// Landing page completa - HTML con estilos inline
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Carlos Castaño - Machine Learning Engineer & Data Science Leader. Portafolio con proyectos de MLOps, sistemas de recomendación, detección de fraude en tiempo real." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Carlos Castaño - Machine Learning Engineer & Data Science Leader" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Portafolio de Carlos Castaño, Machine Learning Engineer & Data Scientist con experiencia en liderazgo técnico." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://carloscastau.github.io" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="/og-image.png" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Carlos Castaño - Machine Learning Engineer & Data Science Leader" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Portafolio de Carlos Castaño, Machine Learning Engineer & Data Scientist con experiencia en liderazgo técnico." />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="/og-image.png" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
  <title>Carlos Castaño - Machine Learning Engineer & Data Science Leader</title>

  <style>
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    .project-card { transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; }
    .project-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .tag { @apply inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium rounded-full; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">

  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-6">
        <a href="#" class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Carlos Castaño</a>
        <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-8">
          <a href="#about" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Sobre Mí</a>
          <a href="#projects" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Proyectos</a>
          <a href="#contact" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Contacto</a>
        </nav>
        <button class="md:hidden text-gray-600" onclick="document.getElementById('mobile-menu').classList.toggle('hidden')">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div id="mobile-menu" class="hidden md:hidden pb-4">
        <nav class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <a href="#about" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Sobre Mí</a>
          <a href="#projects" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Proyectos</a>
          <a href="#contact" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900">Contacto</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Carlos Castaño</h1>
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-primary-600 font-semibold mb-4">Machine Learning Engineer & Data Science Leader</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Construyo sistemas de ML escalables y lidero equipos que transforman datos en impacto. Especializado en MLOps, arquitectura de datos, y despliegue de modelos en producción.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-10">
          <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">PyTorch</span>
          <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">Kubernetes</span>
          <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">MLOps</span>
          <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">Feature Engineering</span>
          <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">Liderazgo Técnico</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="#projects" class="px-8 py-3 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Ver Proyectos</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/carloscastau" target="_blank" class="px-8 py-3 border-2 border-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded-lg font-medium hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Sobre Mí</h2>
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Ingeniero curioso con hambre de aprendizaje continuo. Combino profundidad técnica en Machine Learning Engineering con visión estratégica para llevar modelos de investigación a producción. Especializado en construir plataformas MLOps escalables, sistemas de recomendación, y soluciones de ML en tiempo real que generan impacto de negocio medible.
          </p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Machine Learning</h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">PyTorch</span>
                <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">TensorFlow</span>
                <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">Scikit-learn</span>
                <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">XGBoost</span>
                <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">NLP</span>
                <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">Computer Vision</span>
                <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">Time Series</span>
                <span class="tag bg-blue-50 text-blue-700">A/B Testing</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">MLOps & Cloud</h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="tag bg-green-50 text-green-700">Kubernetes</span>
                <span class="tag bg-green-50 text-green-700">Docker</span>
                <span class="tag bg-green-50 text-green-700">MLflow</span>
                <span class="tag bg-green-50 text-green-700">Kubeflow</span>
                <span class="tag bg-green-50 text-green-700">Airflow</span>
                <span class="tag bg-green-50 text-green-700">Terraform</span>
                <span class="tag bg-green-50 text-green-700">CI/CD</span>
                <span class="tag bg-green-50 text-green-700">FastAPI</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Cloud & Infra</h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="tag bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">AWS</span>
                <span class="tag bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">GCP</span>
                <span class="tag bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">Azure</span>
                <span class="tag bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">S3</span>
                <span class="tag bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">EKS</span>
                <span class="tag bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">Lambda</span>
                <span class="tag bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">CloudWatch</span>
                <span class="tag bg-purple-50 text-purple-700">Redis</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Liderazgo</h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="tag bg-orange-50 text-orange-700">Team Leadership</span>
                <span class="tag bg-orange-50 text-orange-700">Technical Architecture</span>
                <span class="tag bg-orange-50 text-orange-700">Mentorship</span>
                <span class="tag bg-orange-50 text-orange-700">Agile</span>
                <span class="tag bg-orange-50 text-orange-700">Cross-functional Collaboration</span>
                <span class="tag bg-orange-50 text-orange-700">Strategic Planning</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Projects Section -->
    <section id="projects" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Proyectos Destacados</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

          <!-- Project 1 -->
          <article class="project-card bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sistema de Recomendación con Feature Store y Monitoreo de Drift</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Sistema de recomendación de productos escalable con feature store centralizado, monitoreo de data drift, y actualización diaria de modelos.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap mb-4">
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Python</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">PyTorch</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Feature Store</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">MLOps</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Kubernetes</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Airflow</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">MLflow</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <a href="https://github.com/carloscastau/recommendation-system" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">Código →</a>
              <a href="#recommendation-case" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">Caso de estudio →</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Project 2 -->
          <article class="project-card bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Plataforma de MLOps para Despliegue Automático de Modelos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Plataforma enterprise de MLOps que automatiza el ciclo de vida completo de modelos ML, desde entrenamiento hasta serving, con rollback automático.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap mb-4">
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Kubernetes</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Docker</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">CI/CD</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">MLOps</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">FastAPI</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Kubeflow</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Terraform</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">AWS</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <a href="https://github.com/carloscastau/mlops-platform" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">Código →</a>
              <a href="#mlops-case" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">Caso de estudio →</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <!-- Project 3 -->
          <article class="project-card bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sistema de Detección de Fraude en Tiempo Real con Feature Engineering Distribuido</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Sistema de fraude real-time procesando 10K transacciones/segundo con feature engineering en streaming y modelos de online learning para adaptación continua.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap mb-4">
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Python</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Apache Flink</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Redis</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Online Learning</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Imbalanced Data</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Scikit-learn</span>
              <span class="tag bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 mr-2 mb-2">Kafka</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <a href="https://github.com/carloscastau/fraud-detection-realtime" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">Código →</a>
              <a href="#fraud-case" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">Caso de estudio →</a>
            </div>
          </article>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="py-20">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">¿Interesado en colaborar?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Estoy abierto a oportunidades de liderazgo técnico en ML/Data Science. Conectemos para discutir cómo puedo aportar valor a tu equipo.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://mx.linkedin.com/in/carloscastau-machinelearning" target="_blank" class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="mailto:ccastanourrego@gmail.com" class="px-6 py-3 border-2 border-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded-lg font-medium hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors">Email</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
        <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            ¿Revisando mi código? Todos mis proyectos están en
            <a href="https://github.com/carloscastau" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-800 font-medium">
              github.com/carloscastau
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm mt-8 md:mt-0">
          <p>© 2024 Carlos Castaño. Construido con Astro y Tailwind.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>